Then WHY are you wasting your money on Insurance?
How much money did you spend on Insurance in the last 12 months?
How much did you receive in payouts?
You could have gone out for dinner and drinks with that money
Then on the rare instance of a lost or broken item
you can do an instant payout &gt;&gt; No Fuss &gt;&gt; No Muss &gt;&gt; No forms to fill out &gt;&gt; No Cooperation needed from the Buyer

