<post author="garmentvarmint" datetime="2012-02-15T15:29:00" id="p3">
WEDGE...

By any chance is this buyer also a direct competitor of yours? If you have any info showing that he is---you can file a Malicious Bidding Complaint---and hopefully, get this person removed from Ebay. <img src="http://forums.ebay.com/images/emoticons/plain.gif" alt=":|"/>

Other than that, if he is bidding on your items on Auctions, you can cancel his bids for each ID as they show up. (that is, get rid of bids from California.

