WEDGE...

And do not allow a nonpayer to leave you a Negative---as I see on one of your transactions. Always file an Unpaid Item Dispute against non-pays. If they do not pay within the next four days---and Neg---that Neg is REMOVABLE. You just contact Ebay with proof they did not pay, as ask them to delete that Neg. It may take several emails, but eventually, Ebay WILL remove those. <img src="http://forums.ebay.com/images/emoticons/happy.gif" alt=":)"/>
