Canceling cross-promotions If you want to cancel your cross - promotion:

Go to My eBay.

Place your pointer over the Account tab, and then click the Marketing Tools link.

Below the Cross -Promotion heading on the left side of the page, click the Settings link.

Select the Do not cross-promote my items option. Your selection applies to all of your active listings.

