Add free shipping to all your listings. Include the cost of shipping &amp; a small handeling fee into your list price. In the end, it comes out to be the same cost for the buyer, also, if you print your labels, through e-bay, your postage is discounted, delivery confirmation tracking information is automatically uploaded for you and an e-mail is sent to your buyer with the tracking number. It's much easier &amp; less expensive than running to the post office.
3 days after your package is confirmed delivered, your funds are automatically released from Paypal, not 21 days.
You also get an automatic high DSR star rating by offering free shipping. No more dings for high shipping costs.
p.s. the money you save on postage &amp; gas by printing your labels through e-bay you won't have to charge a handeling fee.
